Bob Stephenson (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bob_Stephenson_(actor) 0 Robert J. Stephenson (born May 18, 1967) is an American film and television actor, film producer and screenwriter who is probably best known as Sheriff Jimmy Taylor on the CBS TV series Jericho.
